<div id="settings-index">
  <div class="toolbar">
	  <a class="back">Back</a>
	  <h1>Settings</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="vertical-scroll">
    <div>
      <h2>Created by BandWith.Us</h2>
      <p>Contact <a href="mailto:help@bandwith.us">help@bandwith.us</a> if you are having trouble</p>

      <h2>Data Management</h2>
      <p>If you think your app is out of data, trigger a manual sync to update</p>
      <ul id="settings" selected="true" title="Settings" class="rounded">
      	<% if @msg %><li style="color:#ff0000" align="center"><%=@msg%></li><% end %>
      	<li><%=link_to "Perform Sync", :action => :do_sync%></li>
      </ul>
      <p>If you are having major troubles with the application you can reset the database, and pull fresh data</p>
      <ul class="rounded">
      	<li><%=link_to "Reset Database", :action => :reset%></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>